{"tid":978712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"慈雲山米飯主題餐廳","createTime":"2019-01-12T06:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T07:05:36.000Z","uid":105485,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc6827ada4ff1ff4b534dc6ae7a3fe839fbbcd3","tid":978712,"uid":105485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n愈整愈難食<br />\n叫左個鐵板牛肉飯凍華田<br />\n抄又唔撚抄好啲<br />\n鐵板又唔夠熱 啲牛熟唔撚哂<br />\n用個照燒汁隻味又奇怪<br />\n啲牛有70%係肥肉<br />\n杯凍華田追兩次先有<br />\n飲左一啖 嘩屌你淡撚過水<br />\n唔知啲廚房做乜尻<br />\n食到好撚嬲<br />\n仲有啲想嘔想嘔咁<br />\n<br />\n食完先想屌所以冇圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f984adcdcc0a4bc0b5a83db241a812732010f8e7","tid":978712,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"塊魚柳細左一半"},{"pid":"6485c254a44af57658dee4c228af17339c293b21","tid":978712,"uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"燒山個間？"},{"pid":"4ee890605bc8fba407ad5c21a2aedd89ce5acb53","tid":978712,"uid":189983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"果間d野不嬲劣wo,d米食過兩次都好生就唔食鳥"},{"pid":"8eca74e7ff864838b9c40e17286ed503ca3347ab","tid":978712,"uid":105485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f984adcdcc0a4bc0b5a83db241a812732010f8e7","tid":978712,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"塊魚柳細左一半"},"citedBy":0,"rep